    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@rjmholt I would expect `ConvertTo-Json -AsArray 1,2` to return `[[1,2]]`. There are plenty of APIs that accept an array of arrays where the outer array may contain 0 or more inner arrays. \r\n\r\nThe current behavior of `ConvertTo-Json 1,2` is `[1,2]` which means when I need to send `[[1,2]]` I have to do some string manipulation of my own.",
